Class MapDecorator<K,V>

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
CaseInsensitiveMap, MultiValueMap
public class MapDecorator<K,V>
extends Object
implements Map<K,V>, FullMap<K,V>

Contains another map, which is uses as its basic source of data, possibly transforming the data along the way. This class itself simply overrides all methods of Map with versions that pass all requests to the contained map. Subclasses may further override some of these methods and may also provide additional methods and fields.
